{"tid":1743263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我地救唔到佢地出泥，我地一齊入去陪佢地得唔得？","createTime":"2019-11-21T06:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T06:37:39.000Z","uid":191688,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"16768a2d0ed7c7283317e545576d119dcef850c9","tid":1743263,"uid":191688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:26:32.000Z","msg":"我廢 我堅持唔到最後<br />\n而家佢地係入面同便衣狗玩捉衣因<br />\n又唔夠水唔夠食物<br />\n我地幫唔到佢地搵方法走<br />\n咁我地可唔可以一齊入去陪佢地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人多係咪就係安全</span><br />\n<br />\n我見啲議員都入得去<br />\n點解我地唔入得"},{"pid":"cbee269f6f703291703a4b8af0528ce72f4ad458","tid":1743263,"uid":191688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:27:06.000Z","msg":"推 可唔可以呀<br />\n我唔想掉低佢地呀"},{"pid":"afde673070ee0e0719e8acc265d3e1cf5fe72e07","tid":1743263,"uid":191688,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:27:31.000Z","msg":"一齊入去陪佢地得唔得"},{"pid":"c51ac26dc169ca2e5cfdb91662448e47f295e80d","tid":1743263,"uid":62523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:27:44.000Z","msg":"智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ebdf877ba9928fa9bdd338922dba5867898722","tid":1743263,"uid":264091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:28:37.000Z","msg":"你入到去點解佢地唔可以出泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e325912a5fa7ca62a1c5b32890564547da7484","tid":1743263,"uid":111723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:30:06.000Z","msg":"你個腦比車撞過？"},{"pid":"3a9255f1b612f7fc405944d0cef435007c9dc307","tid":1743263,"uid":28